oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Edd Casey performs three songs
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Edd Casey performs an original song, The Memoir Of Jimmie Rodgers, followed by the Jimmie Rodgers songs T.B. Blues and a version of Blue Yodel No. 1 (T For Texas).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Edd Casey
